        "briefDescription": "The scheme aims to increase the storage capacity of perishable products by providing grant assistance for cold storage facilities.\n",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme “Special Scheme for Increasing the Storage Capacity of Perishable Products” launched by the Horticulture and Food Processing Department, Government of Madhya Pradesh, aims to increase cold storage capacity through providing 50% grant assistance to all eligible farmers.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n  - Grant Assistance: A grant of 50% of the project cost up to a maximum of ₹2,00,00,000/- for cold storage facilities up to 5,000 metric tons capacity.\n\n<br>\n\n",
